      Classes in gaffer.accumulostore.retriever.impl that implement CloseableIterable 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  AccumuloAllElementsRetriever
      This allows queries for all elements.
      class  AccumuloIDBetweenSetsRetriever
      Given two sets of EntitySeeds, called A and B, this retrieves all Edges where one end is in set A and the other is in set B and also returns Entitys for EntitySeeds in set A.
      class  AccumuloIDWithinSetRetriever
      Retrieves Edges where both ends are in a given set of EntitySeed's and Entitys where the vertex is in the set.
      class  AccumuloRangeIDRetriever
      This allows queries for all data from between the provided ElementSeed pairs.
      class  AccumuloSingleIDRetriever
      This allows queries for all data related to the provided ElementSeeds.
